titles.title: A concurrent resolution commending NASA Langley Research Center in Virginia on the celebration of its 90th anniversary on October 26 and 27, 2007.

action.text: Referred to the Committee on Commerce, Science, and Transportation.

bill.summary:
10/18/2007--Introduced.
Congratulates and commends the men and women of NASA Langley Research Center for their accomplishments and role in inspiring the American people.
